<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 03:14:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国称欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的草案带来“巨大风险和不确定性”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eu-draft-tariffs-chinese-evs-brings-enormous-risks-uncertainty-2024-08-21/</link><description>据中央电视台周三报道，中国汽车工业协会表示坚决反对欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收高额关税的最终草案。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 02:56:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eu-draft-tariffs-chinese-evs-brings-enormous-risks-uncertainty-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>美联储称，随着投资者关注美国就业机会，股市失去动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-21/</link><description>由于世界股市的强劲反弹暂停，亚洲股市周三下跌，而债券收益率和美元在美国经济数据和政策制定者发表讲话之前下跌，预计将有理由降息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 02:17:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称正在调查被指控与中国犯罪有关的前市长越狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-probing-escape-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-2024-08-21/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，菲律宾政府正在调查被指控与中国犯罪集团有联系的前市长郭爱丽如何设法逃离该国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-probing-escape-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>杰克逊霍尔（Jackson Hole）交易员等待就业数据，美元兑欧元跌至今年最低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hits-lowest-this-year-vs-euro-traders-brace-jobs-data-jackson-hole-2024-08-21/</link><description>周三，美元兑欧元跌至今年以来的最低点，交易员们准备迎接当天晚些时候美国非农就业数据可能出现的重大修正，随后美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔将在本周末发表讲话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hits-lowest-this-year-vs-euro-traders-brace-jobs-data-jackson-hole-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国青年失业率上升催生新工人阶级：“烂尾孩子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rotten-tail-kids-chinas-rising-youth-unemployment-breeds-new-working-class-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国不断上升的失业率正迫使数以百万计的大学毕业生陷入艰难的讨价还价，其中一些人被迫接受低薪工作，甚至靠父母的养老金维持生计，这种困境催生了新的工人阶级“烂尾孩子”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rotten-tail-kids-chinas-rising-youth-unemployment-breeds-new-working-class-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在区域会议前支持斐济总理的太平洋计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-backs-fijian-pms-pacific-plan-ahead-regional-meeting-2024-08-21/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周二在北京举行的一次会议上对来访的斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡表示，他支持他的“和平海洋”计划，几天后，太平洋岛国领导人将在汤加举行峰会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-backs-fijian-pms-pacific-plan-ahead-regional-meeting-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>条款清单显示，沃尔玛寻求通过出售京东股份筹集至多37.4亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/walmart-seeks-raise-374-bln-sale-jdcom-stake-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-20/</link><description>据路透社周三看到的一份投资意向书显示，美国零售商沃尔玛正寻求通过出售其在中国电子商务公司京东的股份筹集至多 37.4 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 23:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/walmart-seeks-raise-374-bln-sale-jdcom-stake-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着市场整合，两次利率电话即将召开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 21:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>美国称秘密核战略不是针对单一国家或威胁的回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-approved-secret-nuclear-strategy-focusing-chinese-threat-new-york-times-2024-08-20/</link><description>在《纽约时报》报道称白宫调整了美国威慑战略，将重点放在中国扩张核武力量之后，白宫周二表示，今年乔·拜登总统批准的机密核战略计划并不是针对单一国家或威胁的回应。阿森纳第一次。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:53:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-approved-secret-nuclear-strategy-focusing-chinese-threat-new-york-times-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>美国在华临床试验遭美国议员质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-clinical-trials-china-questioned-by-us-lawmakers-2024-08-20/</link><description>周二，一个两党议员小组呼吁拜登政府加强对在中国进行的美国临床试验的审查，理由是知识产权被盗的风险以及维吾尔人被迫参与的可能性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 17:07:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-clinical-trials-china-questioned-by-us-lawmakers-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国Antfin持有印度Zomato近一半股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-antfin-nearly-halves-stake-indias-zomato-2024-08-20/</link><description>交易所数据显示，阿里巴巴集团旗下 Antfin 新加坡公司周二出售了印度 Zomato 价值 477.2 亿卢比（合 5.7 亿美元）的股份，将其在这家食品和杂货配送平台的持股比例减少了近一半，至 2.2%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-antfin-nearly-halves-stake-indias-zomato-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>宝马中国产电动Mini将享受21.3%的低关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-china-made-electric-mini-receive-lower-213-tariff-2024-08-20/</link><description>宝马表示，其在中国生产电动Mini的合资企业在欧盟最新的中国制造电动汽车关税文件草案中被列为“合作公司”，有资格享受21.3%的较低关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmws-china-made-electric-mini-receive-lower-213-tariff-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，香港SVI关闭了专注于中国的对冲基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-svi-winds-down-china-focused-hedge-fund-say-sources-2024-08-20/</link><description>三名消息人士称，总部位于香港的对冲基金战略愿景投资（SVI）已缩减其投资于中国股票的主要价值乘数基金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 12:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-svi-winds-down-china-focused-hedge-fund-say-sources-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称被指控与中国犯罪有关的前市长已逃离该国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-has-fled-country-2024-08-20/</link><description>菲律宾一个城镇的一名前市长因涉嫌与中国犯罪集团有联系而接受调查，她已逃离该国，促使菲律宾总统办公室周一下令吊销她的护照。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-has-fled-country-2024-08-20/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中信、中金等10家券商被纳入中国大湾区财富计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/citic-cicc-among-10-brokerages-included-chinas-greater-bay-area-wealth-scheme-2024-08-20/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，中国和香港将扩大试点财富计划，允许居民进行跨境投资，首批 10 家证券公司将加入其中，其中包括中国最大的券商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/citic-cicc-among-10-brokerages-included-chinas-greater-bay-area-wealth-scheme-2024-08-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>